This is a html , css and php project based on hostel management system that u can use on college projects and in others also .
Basically to run this u need wamp(windows) and lamp(linux) .
put this folder inside the www folder in wamp and in linux put in opt/lampp/htdocs .
The sql database is given here so no need to create exrta .
Just opean php my admin and run the sql command there .
Now start wamp or lampp and open the index.php .
So , You Are Ready To GO .
